<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta lang="pt-br">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.6.0/dist/jquery.slim.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
        <title>Página Produto</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <header class="row mx-auto my-auto p-1">
            <div class="col-sm-2 my-auto">
                <img src="../imagens/logovideo.png" class="w-50 mt-4 mb-0">
            </div>  
            <div class="col-sm-8 text-center my-auto">
                <h1 class="font-weight-bold mt-4 mb-0" style="font-size:30px; color:#5A18C9">SEU CONTEÚDO FAVORITO ESTÁ AQUI<BR>QUANDO QUISER E ONDE ESTIVER</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-2 my-auto">
            </div>  
        </header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-light mb-2">
            <hr style="height:1px; width:100%; border-width:0; background-color:#5A18C9">
            <form class="form-inline mx-auto">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="/Home"><button class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm" type="button">Home</button></a>                    
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="/Produtos"><button class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm" type="button">Produtos</button></a>
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="/Promocoes"><button class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm" type="button">Promoções</button></a>                    
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="/Contato"><button class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm" type="button">Contato</button></a>
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="Carrinho"><button class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm" type="button">Carrinho</button></a>                    
            </form>
        </nav>  
        <section class="container">
            <h1 class="text-center" style="background-color:#E0D1FA ;"><b>Descrição do Produto Escolhido</b></h1>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-12 mt-3 text-dark">
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Consequatur ex optio quidem a nesciunt veritatis nemo sint. Est, aperiam? Neque, minus dolor nostrum facilis sunt in amet reprehenderit assumenda numquam suscipit deserunt, odio debitis dolore doloremque maxime voluptate inventore libero modi cum perspiciatis asperiores. Incidunt voluptate harum odio fugiat nemo!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">

                <div class="livro col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-lg-12">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img class="card-img-top w-25" src="imagens/<%=galeria[0].imagem_fi%>" alt="Card image cap">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h4 class="card-title"><%=galeria[0].titulo_fi%></h4>
                            <p class="card-text"><%=galeria[0].sinopse_fi%></p>
                            <h2>R$ <%=galeria[0].valor_fi%></h2>
                            <a href="carrinhoCompra/?id=<%=galeria[0].filmes_id%>" class="btn btn-primary">Adicionar ao carrinho</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>


            <div class="row mt-2 pb-2 text-center" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-radius: 12px;">
                <div class="col-sm-3 mt-3 mb-1 mx-auto">
                    <h2>TITULO</h2>
                    <h2 id="tituloFilme" class="mb-1">Filme Escolhido</h2>
                    <img id="img" class="mx-auto" style="width:fit-content;" src="" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 mt-3 mx-auto">
                    <section>
                        <h2>TRAILER</h2>
                        <div class="mt-5 embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
                            <iframe width="560" height="315" class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VUi2OHA0_sw" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-3 mt-3 mx-auto">
                    <h2 class="mb-5">SINOPSE</h2>
                    <p id="sinopseFilme" class="text-dark text-left"></p>
                    <div class="align-items-end row">
                        <div class="col-sm-4 mt-1">
                            <input id="quantidade" class="form-control my-auto mx-auto" type="number" min='1' max='5'>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-8">
                            <button onclick="btnClick()" id="btnAdd" class=" w-100 btn btn-danger" type="button">Adicionar ao Carrinho</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div id="relacionados" class="row mt-5">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <footer class="bg-dark p-4 text-warning text-center mt-4">
            <p>&copy;2022 - Todos os direitos reservados</p>
        </footer>
    </body>
    <script src="../js/singlePreferencia.js"></script>
</html>